{
  "stem": "25651.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The [NON-ENGLISH] is a little bird, you see, sparrow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But when somebody looked it up in a, in a dictionary of Hebrew, the dictionary said 'swallow.'",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were called The Swallows in Czech.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when the Germans asked about, you know, our football team, we had an emblem of the swallow.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We are The Swallows.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we knew it was freedom.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So there was this sort of undercurrent that we were in a prison.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 2 SECONDS] the objective of the teaching, and of the whole games that were arranged-- football, sport and so on-- [PAUSES FOR 2 SECONDS] the whole policy was to remove the children from the prison atmosphere, and to create an atmosphere in this school as if it's a public school.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, you're, you're boarding in a public school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was very formative for many of us, including me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We think of it fondly, and the girls, as well.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, there were two girls' schools like this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 2 SECONDS] You talked to the girls of these different Jugendheims, and you talk to the children who were not in the Jugendheims, who were with their parents.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were very much hard done by, like Harry Lowett, or Helmut Spritzer.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They weren't in the Jugendheim.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Harry Lowett because he was, somehow-- he couldn't leave his mother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "His mother got hysterical or something I don't know how.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But there were, there were cases, exceptions.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But mainly, the Jugendheim was the place to be, because it was-- the other children that weren't in the Jugendheim envied us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, every day.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Every evening, we met as a family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 1 SECOND] Leo, my brother [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Melosh ?], my aunt, my sister-in-law [INAUDIBLE], and my mother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now Proteczia was one thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
